_sText:
The map was designed with competitive 5v5 play in mind, however, it's a large map (similar to de_season), so it will play perfectly fine with 16v16 as well. As you can see, this is a release candidate, so feedback is very much appreciated. If you were to find any bugs, please post them here, or message me on Steam at http://steamcommunity.com/id/davs-/.

If you add this to your server, please post your IP, or PM it to me and I'll add it to my favorites and try to get people to join your server
